text: Snat n tezlatin seg usaru, Timesliwt (Imeslab Yettargun) d Temdint n Yitran, ddant-d di tefranin n tezlit taxlaft tamawayt. Astidyu Awwur n Yizmawen yedda-d yisem-is di 26 n tefranin - ugar n yal astidyu niḍen.
translated_text: Kabyle: Snat n tezlatin seg usaru, Timesliwt (Imeslab Yettargun) d Temdint n Yitran, ddant-d di tefranin n tezlit taxlaft tamawayt. Astidyu Awwur n Yizmawen yedda-d yisem-is di 26 n tefranin - ugar n yal astidyu niḍen. English: The ugar n yal astidyu niάσση.

text: Ticlemt tzur azal n 70 km si tama iqaṛben 100km si tama ibaɛden.
translated_text: Kabyle: Ticlemt tzur azal n 70 km si tama iqaṛben 100km si tama ibaɛden. English: The distance between the two cities is about 70 km.

text: Akkin ɣer unẓul d Aceṛcuṛ n Nyagara ma deg ugafa tella cbaḥa tagamant ur nettwasexdem ara n Muskuka akked wayen illan deffir-s.

text: Tamurt Ellswurt d tamnaḍt yellan deg unẓul n Tzegzirt, i wumi d yezzi Ilel Bellingshawsen.
translated_text: Kabyle: Tamurt Ellswurt d tamnaḍt yellan deg unẓul n Tzegzirt, i wumi d yezzi Ilel Bellingshawsen. English: The Book of the Dead.

text: Abrid n Tezgelt n Unẓul (neɣ Abrid Arurad) d amecwaṛ n 1600 km si Teɣsert MakMurdu deg Yilel Russ ɣer Tezgelt.
translated_text: Kabyle: Abrid n Tezgelt n Unẓul (neɣ Abrid Arurad) d amecwaṛ n 1600 km si Teɣsert MakMurdu deg Yilel Russ ɣer Tezgelt. English: Abrid n Tezgelt n Unẓul (neɣ Abrid Arurad) d amecwaṛ n 1600 km si Teɣsert MakMurdu deg Yilel Russ dhal.

text: Illa nnig n yiri n ugafa n Maču Biču udrar-agi isaksren mliḥ, id-itteddun s umata deffir n waṭas n tugniwin n rmim.
translated_text: Kabyle: Illa nnig n yiri n ugafa n Maču Biču udrar-agi isaksren mliḥ, id-itteddun s umata deffir n waṭas n tugniwin n rmim. English: The night is the night of the moon.

text: Enseladus d taɣawsa i d-yettarran tafat akk deg unagraw afuktan, tettarra-d tamudi n 90 n ufmiḍi n tafat n yiṭij i d-yettilin fell-as.
translated_text: Kabyle: Enseladus d taɣawsa i d-yettarran tafat akk deg unagraw afuktan, tettarra-d tamudi n 90 n ufmiḍi n tafat n yiṭij i d-yettilin fell-as. English: The Enseladus of Taɣwsa.

text: Ur yelli wayen tzemreḍ ad twaliḍ niḍen siwa igenni, yeṣfan ahuskan nnig-is d yidurar is-d-yezzin. Ciṭ maḍi seg umaḍal-agi i wumi tzemreḍ ad twaliḍ neɣ ad tesleḍ si daxel n yifri.
translated_text: Kabyle: Ur yelli wayen tzemreḍ ad twaliḍ niḍen siwa igenni, yeṣfan ahuskan nnig-is d yidurar is-d-yezzin. Ciṭ maḍi seg umaḍal-agi i wumi tzemreḍ ad twaliḍ neɣ ad tesleḍ si daxel n yifri. English: The word is used to describe the process of making a cloth.

text: Tura ad nezzi ɣer Jabu. Jabu d tamurt tigzirt, am Briṭanya.
translated_text: Kabyle: Tura ad nezzi ɣer Jabu. Jabu d tamurt tigzirt, am Briṭanya. English: The King of the Mountains.

text: Deg tqacuct-is, Tabuciḍant Tanabgast Gunu, yettusemman ɣef ucekkaṛ n yifrrawen n tezdayt deg tutlayt n Maldif, teṣṣaweḍ ad telḥu s waḍu n 240 n yikilumitren deg yiwen n usrag (149 n yimaylen deg usrag).

text: Tigzirin n Cetland n Unẓul, i d-ufan di 1819, ssutren-tent-id waṭas n yeɣlanen yerna deg-sent tuget n yezdaren, s mraw d seddis gar-asen d aganen di 2020.
